headline: Duke Energy celebrates Black History Month with $50,000 in grants directed to organizations by company's South Carolina employees
summary: To celebrate Black History Month, Duke Energy's South Carolina employees have awarded $50,000 in grants to nonprofit organizations whose focus is uplifting, educating and assisting local communities.

headline: Duke Energy Recognizes Significant Economic Development Growth in Ohio and Kentucky
summary: CINCINNATI, OH / ACCESS Newswire / February 25, 2025 / Duke Energy recently announced the recipients of its 2024 Duke Energy Economic Development Awards, which recognize communities and individuals that continually support growth and economic development ...
